38:09.491 --> 38:10.431
-Alright?
-Yep.

38:10.531 --> 38:12.031
NATALIE: What are they
gonna do to her?

38:12.131 --> 38:14.671
They're gonna take a vein from
her leg, graft it into her arm

38:14.771 --> 38:16.271
so they can get
the blood flowing.

38:16.371 --> 38:18.952
OK, Nicole, just hold tight
for me. Alright?

38:19.052 --> 38:21.972
-NATALIE: OK, squeeze my hand.
-Just gonna open this up, OK?

38:22.972 --> 38:24.352
(NICOLE GROANS)

38:24.452 --> 38:26.032
(NICOLE BREATHES DEEPLY)

38:26.132 --> 38:28.792
Oh, I swear to God
if I could get up,

38:28.892 --> 38:31.192
I'd kick you
in the goddamn head!

38:31.292 --> 38:33.472
(CHUCKLES) I'm glad
you can't get up, then.

38:33.572 --> 38:35.793
-I'll be right back, OK?
-NATALIE: Thank you.

38:35.893 --> 38:39.393
Hey, hey. It's gonna... It's
gonna get better soon now, OK?

38:39.493 --> 38:41.233
(NICOLE BREATHES DEEPLY)

38:41.333 --> 38:42.753
It's gonna be OK.

38:42.853 --> 38:46.553
(NICOLE BREATHES DEEPLY)

38:46.653 --> 38:49.233
It's gonna be OK.
We're gonna go home.

38:49.333 --> 38:51.333
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

38:52.774 --> 38:54.894
(EERIE MUSIC)

39:06.534 --> 39:09.975
(WOMAN CRIES LOUDLY)
I can't stand up!

39:19.135 --> 39:21.235
MAN: Endang.

39:21.335 --> 39:22.835
Endang.

39:31.776 --> 39:32.716
(ENDANG CRIES)

39:32.816 --> 39:34.816
MAN:

39:41.936 --> 39:43.937
Gede!

39:44.857 --> 39:46.857
Gede!

39:49.617 --> 39:51.757
(WOMAN GASPS)

39:51.857 --> 39:53.857
(CRIES)

39:57.377 --> 39:59.378
Gede!

39:59.978 --> 40:01.978
Gede!

40:06.298 --> 40:08.298
Gede!

40:14.858 --> 40:17.039
Gede!

40:17.139 --> 40:18.839
Gede, Ni Luh...

40:18.939 --> 40:20.939
Gede!

40:24.379 --> 40:26.379
Gede!

40:28.939 --> 40:30.479
(NI LUH CRIES)

40:30.579 --> 40:32.580
Gede! (CRIES)

40:37.980 --> 40:39.600
(CONTINUES CRYING)

40:39.700 --> 40:41.700
(SOMBRE MUSIC)

40:54.341 --> 40:56.081
MAN: Do we know the scale?

40:56.181 --> 40:59.321
MAN 2: Uh, reports vary.
Anything from 20 dead, maybe 50.

40:59.421 --> 41:01.081
We just don't know.

41:01.181 --> 41:02.641
What happened?

41:02.741 --> 41:04.841
It's not clear.
Most probably a bomb.

41:04.941 --> 41:06.202
Our first priority

41:06.302 --> 41:08.082
is to get the injured
back here to Australia.

41:08.182 --> 41:09.402
I've mobilised the RAAF.

41:09.502 --> 41:11.602
I need you on the first plane
over there.

41:11.702 --> 41:12.882
To do what?

41:12.982 --> 41:14.842
Oversee and manage
the situation.

41:14.942 --> 41:17.442
I need you to collect evidence,
identify the dead.

41:17.542 --> 41:20.782
Friends, I need this room now.
Please? Thank you.

41:23.463 --> 41:26.363
I need you to find out
what happened.

41:26.463 --> 41:29.123
You'll head up
the Australian side

41:29.223 --> 41:31.603
of the Indonesian-Australian
joint strike force.

41:31.703 --> 41:34.283
Do we know who I will be working
with on the Indonesian side?

41:34.383 --> 41:36.043
We've not yet heard.

41:36.143 --> 41:37.443
We actually don't have approval

41:37.543 --> 41:39.243
for you to be there
from the Indonesians yet.

41:39.343 --> 41:41.084
We're working on that.
Mick Keelty will call you.

41:41.184 --> 41:44.204
Did Foreign Affairs
have any warning?

41:44.304 --> 41:46.524
Was there any chatter?

41:46.624 --> 41:48.724
No. No, completely
out of the blue.

41:48.824 --> 41:51.224
You have my number.
Keep me posted.

41:53.224 --> 41:55.224
(PHONE BEEPS)

42:51.988 --> 42:54.348
REPORTER ON TV:

43:10.349 --> 43:12.349
(REPORTER CONTINUES ON TV)

43:59.632 --> 44:01.632
What did we do wrong?

44:11.353 --> 44:13.373
(SOLDERING SIZZLES)

44:15.673 --> 44:17.673
(TENSE MUSIC)

44:27.154 --> 44:29.234
(TENSE MUSIC BUILDS)
